data.description: The "WOW" feeling you've been waiting for! Nearly new, 3/2 Ranch home w/office that could be used as a 4th bedroom.Offering over 2200 Sq Ft of living space,1st floor laundry,& 3 car garage. Showcasing a seamless blend of modern design & comfort, crafted to elevate your lifestyle.You'll enjoy the grandeur of 9ft ceilings, accentuated by elegant tray ceilings in the family & dining rooms.The spacious layout creates an inviting atmosphere, that easily transitions from quiet evenings scrolling your favorite socials by the fireplace, to prime real estate for hosting dinner/cocktail parties or special events.Huge lower level w/walkout provides the next lucky owner an opportunity to finish the space utilizing their personal vision. Modern, minimalist landscape design; w/"golf course worthy" turf & large deck. Appliances, mechanics & roof less than 4 years old. Unbeatable location; close to all the hot spots in Liberty Center, VoA park, Miami University Hamilton, & highways.Lakota Local SD!
